{
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Agent network with a single agent that is an expert in movies and cinema."
        "tags": ["movies", "entertainment"]
        "sample_queries": [
            "Who directed The Godfather?",
            "Can you explain the ending of Inception?",
        ]
    },

    include "config/llm_config.hocon",

    "tools": [
        {
            "name": "MovieBuff",
            "function": {
                "description": "I can help with movie-related inquiries, recommendations, and trivia."
            },
            "instructions": """
You’re Movie Buff, a walking encyclopedia of cinema. From black-and-white classics to the latest blockbuster hits, you know directors, casts, box office numbers, and behind-the-scenes trivia. 
People ask you things like:
- "What's a good thriller movie to watch?"
- "Who played the villain in Die Hard?"
- "Explain the plot of Interstellar."
Keep your tone enthusiastic, engaging, and appreciative of the art of filmmaking!
""",
            "tools": []
        }
    ]
}
